data.description: Come and see this spacious and beautiful home in a great location! Near 3 minutes Dell Diamond, the Domain Mall, RR outlets and Kalahari Convention center. Hard tile kitchen, hall & dining area. Granite counter tops, fireplace, breakfast bar, ceiling fans, spacious bedrooms, large master suite features double sinks on a long vanity, garden tub and separate shower. Walk in closet and big backyard with mature trees.  Home is currently occupied. FHA Loan Assumption is available, don't miss the opportunity on taking a low interest rate mortgage loan. Contact realtor for more information.
